{
  "category": "Phase 1: Production-Grade Foundation",
  "description": "**Milestone:** Phase 1: Production-Grade Foundation\n\nAudit test coverage for all 13 components and write missing tests to achieve 80%+ line coverage per component. Focus on: form-associated behavior (ElementInternals), keyboard navigation, slot projection, CSS part styling, event dispatch, and reactive property updates.\n\n**Files to Modify:**\n- packages/hx-library/src/components/*/hx-*.test.ts\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- [ ] 80%+ line coverage per component\n- [ ] Form-associated components tested with form submission\n- [ ] Keyboard navigation tested for interactive components\n- [ ] Slot projection tested with light DOM content\n- [ ] Event dispatch tested with composed: true where needed\n- [ ] All tests pass in Vitest browser mode (Chromium)\n\n**Complexity:** large",
  "title": "Write missing Vitest browser tests for 80%+ coverage",
  "status": "done",
  "isEpic": false,
